lead_paragraph: Oakland's Chris Coghlan had never seen the unorthodox sidearm delivery of right-hander Steve Cishek from the batter's box until Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Coghlan's Homer in 9th Gives Oakland a 3-2 Win Over Seattle
